{
  "title": "Light Ethiopian Cabbage Soup",
  "description": "A bright, sour, one‑pot soup with shredded cabbage, fermented cabbage, oregano, and a splash of lemon, kosher‑friendly and wonderfully light.",
  "cuisine": "Ethiopian",
