  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a 6‑quart pot over medium heat.",
    "Add diced onion and carrots, sauté until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Stir in minced garlic and oregano, cook for 30 seconds until fragrant.",
    "Add shredded cabbage and fermented cabbage, stir to combine.",
    "Pour in vegetable broth and water, bring to a gentle boil.",
    "Reduce heat, cover, and simmer for 15 minutes until cabbage is tender.",
    "Season with kosher salt and black pepper, adjusting to taste.",
    "Stir in lemon juice, then remove from heat.",
    "Let the soup rest for 5 minutes before serving.",
    "Ladle into bowls, garnish with fresh oregano if desired."
  ],
